docs.abstract: Algorithms are sending ads by American brands onto Russian disinformation sites.
docs.snippet: Algorithms are sending ads by American brands onto Russian disinformation sites.
docs.lead_paragraph: Lenin is sometimes said to have predicted that capitalists would sell Russia the rope with which they would be hanged. Yet not even Lenin could have imagined Vladimir Putin’s success in getting some of the largest Western companies to subsidize his disinformation efforts by advertising on his government-run “news” websites.

docs.abstract: Just a year ago, the world’s richest man seemed to have a pretty low-key life. Times sure have changed.
docs.snippet: Just a year ago, the world’s richest man seemed to have a pretty low-key life. Times sure have changed.
docs.lead_paragraph: SEATTLE — When Jeff Bezos and his former wife, MacKenzie, celebrated what would be their last anniversary together around Labor Day 2018, they arrived at a Miami nightclub with no fanfare. His table was booked online, which is “totally what tourists do” and “totally dorky,” the club’s celebrity liaison said in an interview at the time.

headline.print_headline: Hot Love! Tabloids Embrace New Bezos

docs.abstract: Investigators said the phone of Jeff Bezos, the Amazon chief, began behaving strangely after he received a video from Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman’s WhatsApp account.
docs.snippet: Investigators said the phone of Jeff Bezos, the Amazon chief, began behaving strangely after he received a video from Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman’s WhatsApp account.
docs.lead_paragraph: SEATTLE — A forensic analysis of Jeff Bezos’ cellphone found with “medium to high confidence” that the Amazon chief’s device was hacked after he received a video from a WhatsApp account reportedly belonging to Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman of Saudi Arabia.

headline.main: Analysis Ties Hacking of Bezos’ Phone to Saudi Leader’s Account
headline.print_headline: Inquiry Is Said to Link Hacking of Bezos’ Phone To Saudi Leader’s Account
